<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>refhub sharing email</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/orioncactus/pretendard/dist/web/static/pretendard.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>

<body style="font-family: 'Pretendard', sans-serif; height: 100vh; margin: 0; padding: 0; display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; background-color: #FFFFFF;">
  <div style="max-width: 600px; width: 100%; padding: 40px; background: #FFFFFF; border: 1px solid #F9FAF9; text-align: left; letter-spacing: -1px;">
    <div style="margin-bottom: 5px;">
      <img src="cid:logo" alt="RefHub 로고" style="height: 20px;">
    </div>
    <h1 style="font-size: 1.6rem; color: #282828; margin: 0; margin-bottom: 20px; letter-spacing: -1px;">
      레퍼브 <span style="color: #1ABC9C;"><%= collection %></span> 컬렉션에 함께 하세요!
    </h1>
    <hr style="width: 100px; border: none; border-top: 1.6px solid #FBBC05; margin: 10px 0 20px 0; margin-bottom: 30px;">
    <div style="font-size: 1rem; color: #282828; line-height: 2; margin-bottom: 20px; letter-spacing: -1px;">
      <p><strong><%= owner %></strong> 님이 <strong><%= name %></strong> 님을 <strong><%= collection %></strong> 컬렉션에 초대했습니다.<br>
      <strong><%= collection %></strong> 컬렉션에서 레퍼런스를 같이 공유해보세요.</p>
    </div>
    <p>
      <a href="<%= link %>" style="color: #ffffff !important; background-color: #1ABC9C; border: none; padding: 0.8rem 2rem; font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: bold; border-radius: 10px; cursor: pointer; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; transition: background-color 0.3s ease; color: white; text-align: center; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px;">바로 이동하기</a>
    </p>
    <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: #8A8D8A;">
      * 계정이 없는 경우, 회원가입 후 컬렉션에 접근이 가능합니다.
    </p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
